precis:
Enactment of the NOTICES OF DEPOSITS RESTRICTIONS (AUTHORIZED FOREIGN
BANKS) REGULATIONS which require full-service branches of those banks to
post notices and provide written notices indicating that deposits with the
branch are not insured by the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation.
